<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger; background-color:silver; color:#000;" class="fn summary">Sergei Parajanov<br />
Սարգիս Փարաջանյան</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="padding: 0px; padding-top: 2px; text-align:center; font-size:100%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Parajanov.jpg" class="image" title="Parajanov.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4e/Parajanov.jpg" width="132" height="185" border="0" /></a><br /></td>
